Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.98,dec-CN,NEXTEPTITLE,0,0,0,,純真·邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.89,dec-CN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48}*冒險者工會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:11.73,dec-CN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs42}委託書\N狼人牙齒、交貨一個\N其具備體力恢復\N在西部森林一座橋梁殘骸附近\N經常有人目擊到狼人\N據信附近藏匿著一群狼人\N報酬：兩枚金幣、五枚硬幣\N接單公會：西區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:28.02,dec-CN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs48}委託書\N委託內容：狼人牙齒一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.67,dec-CN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs48}名稱：狼人\N屬性：土  力量：157\N魔力：20  體力：77\N感覺：53  敏捷：205\N合計：512\N步行且團體行動\N中等危險度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.13,dec-CN,SIGN,0,0,0,,合計：512
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.89,dec-CN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs48}奇美拉·原型\N屬性：土  力量：677\N魔力：66  體力：337\N敏捷：621  感覺：162\N合計：1863\N充滿真正和平、使命智慧積蓄\N調和之後一切都被精華\N地學是存在的意義\N「與造物神起源連結」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:59.08,dec-CN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48}名稱：血鋼手套 品質：稀有\N裝備手及腕\N對當權者怨念\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:59.08,dec-CN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs48}裝備此套：\N力量減少82\N魔力減少101\N合計：183
Comment: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:31.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出现钟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:41.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:56.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:01.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:08.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:11.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:16.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:21.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:31.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:35.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:40.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1365.333,91.001)}Aren't you? 明鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:40.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:40.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:50.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:50.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\pos(1184,80)\bord1.2}climb back up unswayed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:58.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru get out
